        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Of the sons of Phinehas — of Ithamar — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "By the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "sons, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "he means the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "families ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "of these two persons, two of which he particularly names, those of Gershom and Daniel: not Daniel the prophet, but some eminent person of Ithamar’s line.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
